Package: corporaexplorer
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny App for Exploration of Text Collections
Version: 0.5.1.9000
Authors@R: person("Kristian Lundby", "Gjerde", email = "kristian.gjerde@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for dynamic exploration of text collections. The
    package contains 1) a helper function to convert a data
    frame to a 'corporaexplorerobject', 2) a Shiny app for fast and flexible
    exploration of a 'corporaexplorerobject', and 3) a Shiny app for simple
    retrieval/extraction of documents from a 'corporaexplorerobject' in a
    reading-friendly format. The intended primary audience
    is qualitatively oriented researchers who rely on close reading of textual
    documents as part of their academic activity.
Depends:
